About This Company
Trust Insurance Brokers (TRUST) has been operating in Saudi Arabia as an independent insurance Broker since 1998, and is one of the first Brokers to receive SAMA (Saudi Arabian Monetary Agency) licensing under the new cooperative insurance laws and regulations of 2008.
Currently, TRUST handles a large reputable client base in various industries, and operates through Jeddah, Riyadh, and Madinah offices, while doing business with all leading licensed insurance companies in the local market. Nonetheless, TRUST employees over 40 professional qualified insurance personnel who successfully serve and manage a portfolio over seventy million Saudi Riyals (USD 20 Million).
